            "documentation": "This ACE code changes the current active swarming pokemon that can be found in the region.\n\nAt midnight, the game rolls a random number from 0-4294967295. The chosen number gives a different current active swarm, there's 28 possible total swarms. 0-27 gives us a different swarm for each number, and that loops every 28 numbers up to the max, so 0 and 28 would both give us doduo.\n\nJust select the swarming pokemon you want to be active, find it in the variables, and put it as the value to be set! (Value is set in hex)\n\n0-doduo\n\n1-zigzagoon\n\n2-cubone\n\n3-nosepass\n\n4-phanpy\n\n5-dunsparce\n\n6-snubbull\n\n7-absol\n\n8-spoink\n\n9-drowzee\n\n10-delibird\n\n11-swinub\n\n12-voltorb\n\n13-farfetch'd\n\n14-skitty\n\n15-natu\n\n16-makuhita\n\n17-krabby\n\n18-spinda\n\n19-beldum\n\n20-pidgey\n\n21-corsola\n\n22-surskit\n\n23-lickitung\n\n24-smoochum\n\n25-electrike\n\n26-slakoth\n\n27-magnemite\n\n"
